All right, it's a bit early, innit? I haven't even had me porridge yet.

37
00:03:37,560 --> 00:03:40,758
来吧，往后站，小伙子，你知道该怎么做。
Come on, stand back, lad, you know the drill.

38
00:03:40,760 --> 00:03:42,960
抓住希特勒漏掉的那几个人！
Get the Yids that Hitler missed!

39
00:03:57,880 --> 00:04:00,120
哦，是的，你当然知道。
Oh, yeah, course you did.

40
00:04:06,800 --> 00:04:09,080
