帮我个忙。
Do me a favour.

42
00:04:20,080 --> 00:04:21,558
你在笑，不是吗？
You're having a laugh, ain't ya?

43
00:04:21,560 --> 00:04:24,998
所罗门-马林诺夫斯基，我以纵火罪嫌疑逮捕你。
Solomon Malinovsky, I'm arresting you on suspicion of arson.

44
00:04:25,000 --> 00:04:27,438
