I'd say he couldn't be in safer hands.

75
00:06:53,240 --> 00:06:56,598
现在，我希望尽快恢复训练... 告诉他。
Now, I want training to resume as soon as possible... Tell him.

76
00:06:56,600 --> 00:06:58,120
去吧，告诉他。
Go on, tell him.

77
00:06:59,800 --> 00:07:01,280
告诉他什么？
Tell him what?

78
00:07:04,040 --> 00:07:05,240
说吧。
Go on.

79
00:07:06,840 --> 00:07:09,918
这并不重要。他要离开他。
It doesn't matter. He was going to leave him.

80
00:07:09,920 --> 00:07:12,518
彼得要离开李，让他死掉。什么？
Peter was going to leave Lee for dead. What?

81
00:07:12,520 --> 00:07:16,320
我不是那个意思。你是什么意思？
I didn't mean it that way. How did you mean it?

82
00:07:17,720 --> 00:07:21,638
老实说，我不是... 你为什么会说那样的话？
Honestly, I wasn't... Why would you say a thing like that?

83
00:07:21,640 --> 00:07:24,360
彼得？你能解释一下吗？
Peter? Care to explain?

84
00:07:27,200 --> 00:07:29,998
我在看守洛克威尔先生，先生。
I was guarding Mr Rockwell, sir.

85
00:07:30,000 --> 00:07:34,158
在他那边事情变得严重之前 然后那些犹太人就开始了猛攻。
Before things got heavy on his side. Then the Yids started storming.

86
00:07:34,160 --> 00:07:38,360
不是吗？如果你记得的话，那是一场混乱。是的。这就对了。
Didn't they? It was mayhem, if you recall. Right. That's right.

87
00:07:39,720 --> 00:07:44,318
杰夫告诉我李受伤了，但我没有看到他。
Jeff told me Lee had been hurt, but I hadn't seen him.

88
00:07:44,320 --> 00:07:46,958
我不知道他处于什么状态。
I didn't know what state he was in.

89
00:07:46,960 --> 00:07:50,558
正是如此。他没有看到他，先生。是的，我并不担心，因为...
Exactly. He hadn't seen him, sir. Yeah, I wasn't worried cos...

90
00:07:50,560 --> 00:07:54,278
...他是个斗士，不是吗？强壮的小伙子。
..he's a fighter, isn't he? Strong lad.

91
00:07:54,280 --> 00:07:57,038
但一看到杰夫的脸，好吧。
But one look at Jeff's face, well,

92
00:07:57,040 --> 00:08:00,558
我就直奔主题了。不是吗，杰夫？
I got straight round there. Didn't I, Jeff?

93
00:08:00,560 --> 00:08:03,878
是的，没错。说实话，这没什么。
You did, yeah. What? Honestly, it's nothing.

94
00:08:03,880 --> 00:08:07,960
你说... 你说感觉不对，这是你说的。
You said... You said it felt off, that's what you said.

95
00:08:11,000 --> 00:08:12,598
好吧，我想当李醒过来的时候，
Well, I suppose when Lee wakes up,

96
00:08:12,600 --> 00:08:14,560
他就能自己告诉我们了，不是吗？
he'll be able to tell us himself, won't he?

97
00:08:17,200 --> 00:08:19,598
是的。正是如此。
Yeah. Exactly.

98
00:08:19,600 --> 00:08:22,040
如果。如果他醒过来，
If. If he wakes up.

99
00:08:23,600 --> 00:08:25,998
简会照顾他。什么？
Jane will nurse him. What?

100
00:08:26,000 --> 00:08:29,358
不，不，不，拜托，不是她。
No, no, no, please, not her.

101
00:08:29,360 --> 00:08:33,438
我有三个姐妹。我明白，你身体里的荷尔蒙
I have three sisters. I understand, the hormones in your body

102
00:08:33,440 --> 00:08:35,878
正在做着惊人的事情。
are doing spectacular things.

103
00:08:35,880 --> 00:08:40,200
