Try not to get yourself in a state. For the baby's sake.

104
00:08:41,600 --> 00:08:46,320
带她去火车站。不，不，请，请。不！
Take her to the train station. No. No, please, please. No!

105
00:09:03,400 --> 00:09:05,080
李，你能听到我吗？
Lee, can you hear me?

106
00:09:10,080 --> 00:09:14,160
李？只是去给你换一下敷料。
Lee? Just going to change your dressings.

107
00:09:21,880 --> 00:09:23,920
对不起，杰夫，我真的很抱歉。
Sorry, Jeff, I'm really sorry.

108
00:09:25,920 --> 00:09:28,280
该死的，杰夫，伙计，等一下。
Damn, Jeff, mate, hang on.

109
00:09:30,720 --> 00:09:32,478
从公爵的图书馆来的。
From the Duke's library.

110
00:09:32,480 --> 00:09:34,758
我很难带着它离开，不是吗？那是偷窃。
Can hardly leave with it, can I? That'd be stealing.

111
00:09:34,760 --> 00:09:37,960
你不会太久的，是吗？两分钟。
You won't be long, will ya? Two minutes.

112
00:09:51,000 --> 00:09:52,600
简，你能来吗？
Jane, can you come?

113
00:09:54,120 --> 00:09:55,640
我不能，彼得。
I can't, Peter.

114
00:09:57,000 --> 00:10:00,000
他们无处不在。来吧，请。
They're everywhere. Just come, please.

115
00:10:04,960 --> 00:10:06,920
是你对他做的吗？
Did you do that to him?

116
00:10:08,680 --> 00:10:12,120
是的。科林知道你是谁，维维安。
Yes. Colin knows who you are, Vivien.

117
00:10:13,080 --> 00:10:16,400
你和那个克莱因男孩。他在《纪事报》上看到了。
You and the Klein boy. He saw it in the Chronicle.

118
00:10:19,280 --> 00:10:22,638
杰里米？你的订婚公告被印在了报纸上。
Jeremy? Your engagement announcement was printed in the paper.

119
00:10:22,640 --> 00:10:26,038
