132
00:11:01,720 --> 00:11:05,918
听我说。听着。无论你昨晚让他对你做什么，
Listen to me. Listen. Whatever you let him do to you last night,

133
00:11:05,920 --> 00:11:08,518
我原谅你，好吗？我可以原谅你...
I forgive you, all right? I can forgive you...

134
00:11:08,520 --> 00:11:11,398
我不是在请求你的原谅，杰克。
I'm not asking for your forgiveness, Jack.

135
00:11:11,400 --> 00:11:13,358
我没有要求什么。
I'm not asking for anything.

136
00:11:13,360 --> 00:11:15,558
你现在需要听从我的领导。
You need to follow my lead now.

137
00:11:15,560 --> 00:11:18,798
