arms invoices, membership files, bank transfers, everything.

139
00:11:22,480 --> 00:11:26,000
我不能让你回去。我要回去了。他们会杀了你的。
I can't let you go back. I'm going back. They'll kill you.

140
00:11:29,960 --> 00:11:31,960
他走了吗？他就来了。
Has he gone? He's coming.

141
00:11:33,960 --> 00:11:38,320
不应该让他走。他要来了！好了吗？
Shouldn't have let him go. HE'S COMING! ALL RIGHT?!

142
00:11:41,040 --> 00:11:42,880
该死的。该死的！
Dammit. Dammit!

143
00:12:01,880 --> 00:12:04,838
你什么时候能玩？快了。
When can you play? Soon.

144
00:12:04,840 --> 00:12:09,080
什么时候吃午饭？我想知道你父亲把那个箱子放在哪里。
When is lunch? I wonder where your father put that suitcase.

145
00:12:10,480 --> 00:12:11,720
保罗？
Paul?

146
00:12:12,960 --> 00:12:15,998
保罗，我在和你说话。什么事？
Paul, I'm talking to you. Yes?

147
00:12:16,000 --> 00:12:18,958
你知道你父亲把那个旧皮箱放在哪里吗？
Do you know where your father put that old suitcase?

148
00:12:18,960 --> 00:12:23,798
不喜欢醋栗。为什么所有的东西都有醋栗呢？
Don't like currants. Why does everything have currants in it?

149
00:12:23,800 --> 00:12:26,480
我知道，我有一个很好的游戏。
I know, I have a great game.

150
00:12:33,000 --> 00:12:34,240
彼得！
Peter!

151
00:12:36,000 --> 00:12:37,240
找到彼得！
Find Peter!

152
