00:31:16,800 --> 00:31:18,680
等等，等一下。
Wait. Hold up.

323
00:31:20,040 --> 00:31:21,800
他还好吗？
Is he all right?

324
00:31:25,080 --> 00:31:28,478
她并不是说... 她不是怕你。
She didn't mean... She wasn't scared of you.

325
00:31:28,480 --> 00:31:31,878
你今天冒着生命危险来这里。谢谢你。
You risked your neck coming here today. Thank you.

326
00:31:31,880 --> 00:31:35,558
说到底，我们都是一样的，不是吗？
At the end of the day we're all the same, ain't we?

327
00:31:35,560 --> 00:31:38,120
不，我们并不完全一样。
No, we're not quite the same.

328
00:31:40,680 --> 00:31:42,360
但也许...
But maybe...

329
00:31:43,720 --> 00:31:46,278
...我们在为同一场战斗而战。
..we're fighting the same fight.

330
00:31:46,280 --> 00:31:48,800
是的。也许我们是。
Yeah. Maybe we are.

331
00:31:54,880 --> 00:31:57,758
如果薇薇安成功了，你会让我知道的，是吗？
You'll let me know if Vivien makes it, won't you?

332
00:31:57,760 --> 00:32:00,480
别等了。快离开这里。
Don't wait around. Get out of here.

333
00:32:19,600 --> 00:32:21,678
有机会搭车去车站吗？
Any chance of a lift to the station?

334
00:32:21,680 --> 00:32:23,880
我上班要迟到了。
I'm late for work.

335
00:32:25,920 --> 00:32:29,960
上车吧。我看看能不能赶上半点。非常感谢你。
Get in. I'll see if I can make the half past. Thank you so much.

336
00:33:27,280 --> 00:33:28,400
杰夫。
Jeff.

337
00:33:30,080 --> 00:33:31,758
帮帮我。
Help me.

338
00:33:31,760 --> 00:33:34,958
请不要让他们杀了我。
Please don't let them kill me.

339
00:33:34,960 --> 00:33:38,440
你把我当成什么人了？我求你了。
What kind of mug do you take me for? I'm begging ya.

340
00:33:39,720 --> 00:33:43,878
让我打开这扇门。你欺骗了我们。
Just let me open this door. You deceived us.

341
00:33:43,880 --> 00:33:45,800
你应该得到应有的报应。
You deserve what's coming to ya.

342
00:33:48,520 --> 00:33:50,518
你不需要他们。
You don't need them.

343
00:33:50,520 --> 00:33:53,838
你不需要他们。我了解你。
You don't need 'em. I know you.

344
00:33:53,840 --> 00:33:56,200
我知道你经历了什么。闭上你的嘴！
I know what you've been through. Shut your trap!

345
00:33:58,920 --> 00:34:01,838
我知道你所过的生活。
I know the life you've lived.

346
00:34:01,840 --> 00:34:05,198
被所有应该关心你的人辜负了。
Let down by everyone who should have cared for ya.

347
00:34:05,200 --> 00:34:08,038
你自己的母亲破坏了你的信任。
Your own mother broke your trust.

348
00:34:08,040 --> 00:34:11,200
你认为这个世界是腐朽的，是来抓你的。
You think the world's rotten, out to get ya.

349
00:34:14,080 --> 00:34:17,758
以你的手艺，你是对的。
With the hand you've been dealt, you'd be right.

350
00:34:17,760 --> 00:34:21,238
你应该对这个世界感到愤怒，当然你应该，但是... ...
You should be furious with the world, course you should, but...

351
00:34:21,240 --> 00:34:23,798
...你不能认为乔丹就是答案。
..you can't think Jordan's the answer.

352
00:34:23,800 --> 00:34:27,478
我会告诉他你在说什么。我会告诉他。
I'll tell him what you're saying. I'll tell him.

353
00:34:27,480 --> 00:34:31,758
你完蛋了，伙计。你完蛋了。他在利用你。
You're done for, mate. You're finished. He's using ya.

354
00:34:31,760 --> 00:34:34,478
你认为他为什么从不弄脏自己的手？
Why do you think he never gets his hands dirty?

355
00:34:34,480 --> 00:34:38,118
他把你当做一个杯子。他不相信他的运气。
He's taking you for a mug. He can't believe his luck.

356
00:34:38,120 --> 00:34:40,200
他在嘲笑你，杰夫。
He's laughing at ya, Jeff.

357
00:34:43,120 --> 00:34:46,918
把车停下来。让我出去。
Stop the van. And let me out.

358
00:34:46,920 --> 00:34:48,400
我相信你。
I believe in you.

359
00:34:50,280 --> 00:34:52,520
你可以做到这一点。让我出去。
You can do this. Let me out.

360
00:35:00,120 --> 00:35:01,520
杰夫！不！
Jeff! No!

361
00:35:57,280 --> 00:36:01,558
呆在你的座位上。不要让一个场景。
Stay in your seat. Don't make a scene.

362
00:36:01,560 --> 00:36:04,400
我会告诉你这是怎么一回事的。
I'll talk you through how this is going to play out.

363
00:36:17,160 --> 00:36:19,638
要茶吗？不，谢谢你。
Tea? No, thank you.

364
00:36:19,640 --> 00:36:20,880
茶？
Tea?

365
00:36:24,680 --> 00:36:28,480
小姐？小姐？你说什么？
Miss? Miss? Excuse me?

366
00:36:30,920 --> 00:36:35,038
你要告诉我是谁让你这样做的。
You're going to tell me who put you up to it.

367
00:36:35,040 --> 00:36:40,398
你要告诉我你知道的一切。彼得在哪里？
You're going to tell me everything you know. Where's Peter?

368
00:36:40,400 --> 00:36:42,200
你把他带到哪里去了？
Where did you take him?

369
00:36:43,560 --> 00:36:47,238
我想那段小小的恋情现在已经结束了。
I think that little love affair is as good as over now,

370
00:36:47,240 --> 00:36:49,160
现在你已经是受损的货物了。
now that you're damaged goods.

371
00:36:52,560 --> 00:36:55,318
你们这种人有个特殊的地方，你知道的。
There's a special place for your kind, you know.

372
00:36:55,320 --> 00:37:00,278
他们用墨水给你做了标记--Feldhure，野战妓女，横在胸前。
They marked you in ink - Feldhure, field whore, across the chest,

373
00:37:00,280 --> 00:37:04,758
放在一个房间里，供士兵们下班后享用。
kept in a room for the soldiers to enjoy after hours.

374
00:37:04,760 --> 00:37:08,878
甚至其他囚犯也会在集中营里向你吐口水。
Even the other inmates would spit at you in the camps.

375
00:37:08,880 --> 00:37:10,960
对你们来说，这一切都结束了。
It's over for all of you.

376
00:37:13,360 --> 00:37:17,080
我想你认为我是站在历史的错误一边的人。
I suppose you think I'm the one on the wrong side of history.

377
00:37:19,560 --> 00:37:22,118
这对你来说很重要，不是吗？
That's got to you, hasn't it?

378
00:37:22,120 --> 00:37:26,158
你们这些人的问题，是否认的问题。
The trouble with you lot, it's the denial.

379
00:37:26,160 --> 00:37:28,238
看看周围。
Look around.

380
00:37:28,240 --> 00:37:29,958
我们无处不在。
We are everywhere.

381
00:37:29,960 --> 00:37:32,478
我们坐在这节车厢里。
We're sitting in this carriage.

382
00:37:32,480 --> 00:37:35,478
我们在下议院里投票。
We're voting in the House of Commons.

383
00:37:35,480 --> 00:37:39,678
我们在工厂里工作，在田间劳作。
We're working in the factories and toiling in the fields.

384
00:37:39,680 --> 00:37:41,998
我们越来越接近
We are getting closer

385
00:37:42,000 --> 00:37:46,918
越来越接近我们分娩的时刻。
and closer to our moment of delivery.

386
00:37:46,920 --> 00:37:49,358
女士们，先生们，我需要你们的关注，请。
Ladies and gentlemen, I need your attention, please.

387
00:37:49,360 --> 00:37:51,038
我现在处境非常危险。
I am in great danger.

388
00:37:51,040 --> 00:37:54,318
坐在我旁边的这个男人不是我的丈夫。他想伤害我
This man sitting next to me is not my husband. He wants to hurt me

389
00:37:54,320 --> 00:37:57,198
我需要一些帮助。亲爱的，请坐下。
and I need some assistance. Darling, do sit down.

390
00:37:57,200 --> 00:38:00,838
求你了。求你了，难道没有人帮助我吗？请原谅我的妻子。
Please. Please, won't someone help me? Excuse my wife.

391
00:38:00,840 --> 00:38:02,838
她感觉不舒服。不，请，请。
She's not feeling well. No, please, please.

392
00:38:02,840 --> 00:38:06,040
下去吧，亲爱的。求你了！求你了！求你了！
Down you go, dear. Please! Please! Please!

393
00:38:07,520 --> 00:38:09,080
求你了？
Please?

394
00:38:13,680 --> 00:38:15,640
一定是失去了你的感觉。
Must be losing your touch.

395
00:38:22,040 --> 00:38:23,798
女士们，先生们。
Ladies and gentlemen,

396
00:38:23,800 --> 00:38:26,678
火车现在的终点站是拉什福德路。
the train now terminates at Rushford Road.

397
00:38:26,680 --> 00:38:29,558
所有变化，所有变化。即将进入拉什福德路。
All change, all change. Coming into Rushford Road.

398
00:38:32,160 --> 00:38:35,240
女士们先生们，列车在此终点站。
Train terminates here, ladies and gentlemen.

399
00:38:48,680 --> 00:38:50,000
请原谅我。
Excuse me.

400
00:38:52,720 --> 00:38:54,160
你忘了这个。
You forgot this.

401
00:38:56,760 --> 00:38:58,160
太感谢了。
Thank you so much.

402
00:39:06,760 --> 00:39:10,160
你能想象一下，如果我干涉了你的家庭？
Can you for a moment imagine if I'd interloped your family?

403
00:39:11,560 --> 00:39:15,398
如果我是那个撒谎、欺骗的人？
If I had been the one to lie, to deceive?

404
00:39:15,400 --> 00:39:18,158
你能想象吗，维维安？
Could you imagine, Vivien?

405
00:39:18,160 --> 00:39:21,518
你当然不能，因为这个世界上唯一被允许的受害者
Of course you can't, because the only victims that are allowed

406
00:39:21,520 --> 00:39:24,000
在这个世界上存在的唯一受害者就是你。
to exist in this world are you.

407
00:39:25,520 --> 00:39:28,038
我所做的一切
All I am doing

408
00:39:28,040 --> 00:39:29,920
是在保护我的儿子。
is protecting my son.

409
00:39:31,680 --> 00:39:34,638
所有这些都是为了他。
All of this is for him.

410
00:39:34,640 --> 00:39:37,478
我所做的一切是为了给他
Everything I do is to give him

411
00:39:37,480 --> 00:39:40,718
一个更好的机会，一个更好的世界。
a better chance, a better world,

412
00:39:40,720 --> 00:39:43,078
一个更公平的世界。
a fairer world.

413
00:39:43,080 --> 00:39:44,920
就这么简单。
It's as simple as that.

414
00:39:47,160 --> 00:39:49,758
你打算怎么做？
What did you intend to do?

415
00:39:49,760 --> 00:39:54,000
让我的孩子反对我，拆散我的家庭？
Turn my child against me, break up my family?

416
00:39:55,800 --> 00:39:59,560
没有必要。它已经破碎了。
There's no need. It's already broken.

417
00:40:05,560 --> 00:40:08,000
如果你保持沉默，你就有机会了。
If you keep quiet, you have a chance.

418
00:40:10,880 --> 00:40:14,118
不，不。我的伙计们都很忠诚。
No, no. Loyal to a fault, my lads are.

419
00:40:14,120 --> 00:40:16,918
只要我说一句话，就不知道他们会对你做什么。
One word from me and there's no telling what they might do to you.

420
00:40:16,920 --> 00:40:19,520
我们不希望这样，是吗？救命啊！
We don't want that, do we? Help!

421
00:40:26,000 --> 00:40:27,200
啊！
Ah!

422
00:40:29,240 --> 00:40:32,240
追上她！快走！
Get after her! Go!

423
00:40:39,520 --> 00:40:41,158
你能把我藏起来吗？
Can you please hide me?

424
00:40:47,080 --> 00:40:48,200
哦！
Oh!

425
00:40:53,320 --> 00:40:54,640
婊子！
Bitch!

426
00:41:01,200 --> 00:41:02,960
把它从她身上拿开！
Get it off her!

427
00:41:05,680 --> 00:41:08,320
不，把她的手拿开。
No! Get her hands off it.

428
00:41:14,200 --> 00:41:15,880
喂，别管她！
Oi, leave her alone!

429
00:41:17,600 --> 00:41:19,320
把你的手从我身上拿开！
Get your hands off me!

430
00:41:22,480 --> 00:41:24,400
这是我的国家！
This is my country!

431
00:41:25,520 --> 00:41:28,678
这是我的国家！
This is my country!

432
00:41:28,680 --> 00:41:31,480
请把我带到里德利路。来吧，亲爱的，跳进去。
Take me to Ridley Road, please. Go on, love, jump in.

433
00:42:11,400 --> 00:42:13,640
哦。薇薇安。
Oh. Vivien.

434
00:42:17,760 --> 00:42:19,040
杰克...
Jack...

435
00:42:20,840 --> 00:42:22,360
...他在哪里？
..where is he?

436
00:42:24,480 --> 00:42:26,240
我很抱歉。
I'm so sorry.

437
00:42:34,160 --> 00:42:37,638
你可以进去了，但她还没有离开床。没事的。
You can go in but she hasn't left the bed. It's all right,

438
00:42:37,640 --> 00:42:41,160
我知道，我知道。可怜的女孩。我来处理吧。交给我吧。
I know, I know. Poor girl. I'll handle it. Leave it to me.

439
00:42:46,640 --> 00:42:48,798
薇薇安？
Vivien?

440
00:42:48,800 --> 00:42:52,638
薇薇安，亲爱的，有人来找你了。
Vivien, love, there's someone here to see you.

441
00:42:52,640 --> 00:42:55,918
你好，我的爱人。只有我。
Hello, my love. Only me.

442
00:42:55,920 --> 00:42:58,920
我完全知道你需要什么。
I know exactly what you need.

443
00:43:01,000 --> 00:43:02,280
好点了吗？
Better?

444
00:43:04,480 --> 00:43:06,278
好多了。
Much better.

445
00:43:06,280 --> 00:43:10,560
更加... ... 有品位。谢谢你，芭芭拉。
More... classy. Thank you, Barbara.

446
00:43:16,640 --> 00:43:20,398
你站在天使的正确一边，我的爱人。
You're on the right side of the angels, my love.

447
00:43:20,400 --> 00:43:23,960
但你的包是一个绝对的耻辱。
But your bags are an absolute disgrace.

448
00:43:26,160 --> 00:43:30,360
等一下。请你拿着那个，爱泼斯坦夫人？
One sec. Could you hold that, please, Mrs Epstein?

449
00:43:31,920 --> 00:43:35,480
薇薇安，我们要把你打扮得漂漂亮亮的。
Vivien, we're going to fix you up good and proper.

450
00:43:36,920 --> 00:43:39,798
...等着他。是的，但要等他来，然后你就知道了。
..Wait for him. Yes, but wait for him and then you'll know,

451
00:43:39,800 --> 00:43:43,198
他会告诉你该怎么做。听你妈妈的话。因为这很有意义。
he'll tell you what to do. Listen to your mum. Because it makes sense.

452
00:43:43,200 --> 00:43:46,158
为了把这个血淋淋的案子弄出来，我已经走到了地狱的深处。
I've been to the depths of hell to get this bloody case out.

453
00:43:46,160 --> 00:43:49,238
薇薇安，语言。我一秒钟都不想再等了。
Vivien, language. I'm not waiting a second longer.

454
00:43:49,240 --> 00:43:50,878
薇薇安，请。
Vivien, please.

455
00:43:50,880 --> 00:43:54,840
谢谢你，琼斯夫人。他们在这里吗？是的。怎么样？爸爸？
Thank you, Mrs Jones. Are they in 'ere? Yes. Well? Daddy?

456
00:43:56,280 --> 00:43:59,118
他们会看到她的。哦，我的神经。
They'll see her. Oh, my nerves.

457
00:43:59,120 --> 00:44:03,398
呃，他的名字是麦克克拉肯侦探。
Er, and his name's Detective MacCracken.

458
00:44:03,400 --> 00:44:07,798
呃，我听说他在特别部门工作，所以他会参加会议的。
Er, I'm told he works in Special Branch, so he'll take the meeting.

459
00:44:07,800 --> 00:44:10,678
哦，薇薇安。她怎么做，大卫，她会马上去吗？
Oh, Vivien. Well, what does she do, David, does she go right away?

460
00:44:10,680 --> 00:44:13,558
好吧，她不能自己去。 我可以，爸爸，我当然可以。我可以，爸爸，我当然可以。
Well, she can't go on her own. I can, Daddy, of course I can.

461
00:44:13,560 --> 00:44:16,158
如果他们扣押证据或以非法侵入的名义逮捕你...
If they seize the evidence or arrest you for trespassing...

462
00:44:16,160 --> 00:44:17,598
这次就不一样了。
It'll be different this time.

463
00:44:17,600 --> 00:44:19,878
我们不能让你自己去。
We can't afford to let you go on your own.

464
00:44:19,880 --> 00:44:25,038
如果我可以的话，我会带她去，但是... 我有前科。
I would take her if I could but... I have a record.

465
00:44:25,040 --> 00:44:29,838
哦！这只是小事，但......这将危及一切。
Oh! It's only minor but... it would jeopardise everything.

466
00:44:29,840 --> 00:44:32,640
会毁了她所有的巨大工作。
It would ruin all her tremendous work.

467
00:44:36,240 --> 00:44:40,160
我去吧。我和你一起去，维维安。
I'll go. I'll go with you, Vivien.

468
00:45:00,240 --> 00:45:02,638
好吗，姐姐？已经有一段时间了。
All right, sis? It's been a while.

469
00:45:02,640 --> 00:45:05,478
他们又把你放出来了，是吗？是的，你知道我 --
They let you out again, then, did they? Yeah, you know me -

470
00:45:05,480 --> 00:45:08,158
我有朋友，欠了人情。
I've got friends, owed favours.

471
00:45:08,160 --> 00:45:11,360
就像孩子们说的那样，这一切都很有趣。
It's all groovy, as the kids say.

472
00:45:38,680 --> 00:45:41,158
下午好，琼斯太太。
Afternoon, Mrs Jones.

473
00:45:41,160 --> 00:45:44,878
伯恩斯先生。恐怕我现在不接待访客。
Mr Burns. I'm afraid I'm not receiving visitors presently.

474
00:45:44,880 --> 00:45:47,198
哦，对不起。我只是路过而已。
Oh, I'm sorry. I was just passing.

475
00:45:47,200 --> 00:45:49,718
只是我们在会议上错过了你。
Only we've missed you at the meeting.

476
00:45:49,720 --> 00:45:53,518
艾瑟尔的维多利亚海绵不那么有弹性了。
Ethel's Victoria sponge isn't quite as bouncy.

477
00:45:53,520 --> 00:45:56,118
我只是想确定你没事，就这样。
Wanted to make sure you were all right, that's all.

478
00:45:56,120 --> 00:45:59,598
非常好，伯恩斯先生。嗯，就像一个人可以做的那样好
Quite all right, Mr Burns. Well, as all right as one can be

479
00:45:59,600 --> 00:46:01,958
遇到这么多麻烦
with all the troubles that are going on.

480
00:46:04,800 --> 00:46:08,038
哦，对不起，我不知道你有客人。
Oh, pardon me, I didn't know you had guests.

481
00:46:08,040 --> 00:46:12,118
我们正在举行葬礼。什么--瓦？丧礼。
We're sitting a shiva. A what-va? A shiva.

482
00:46:12,120 --> 00:46:15,438
为那位失去生命的年轻先生。
For the young gentleman who lost his life.

483
